query.query: {"measures":[["sum","percent"],["last","year"]],"pigql":"q = load \"opportunity5\"; won_this_year = filter q by 'IsWon' == \"true\";won_this_year = filter won_this_year by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year\"..\"current day\"];closed_this_year = filter q by 'IsClosed' == \"true\"; closed_this_year = filter closed_this_year by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year\"..\"current day\"];won_last_year = filter q by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; won_last_year = filter won_last_year by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year - 1 year\"..\"current day - 1 year\"];closed_last_year = filter q by 'IsClosed' == \"true\"; closed_last_year = filter closed_last_year by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year - 1 year\"..\"current day - 1 year\"];result = group won_this_year by all full, closed_this_year by all full, won_last_year by all full, closed_last_year by all;result = foreach result generate sum(won_this_year['Amount']) as 'A', sum(closed_this_year['Amount']) as 'B', sum(won_last_year['Amount']) as 'C', sum(closed_last_year['Amount']) as 'D';result = foreach result generate ((A/B) - (C/D)) / (C/D) as 'sum_percent',(C/D) as 'last_year' ;result = foreach result generate (case when 'sum_percent' < 0 then \"#E3193B\" when 'sum_percent' > 0 then \"#067D1E\" else \"#192B61\" end) as 'color', 'sum_percent' as 'sum_percent','last_year';"}

{"pigql":"a = load \"opportunity5\"; a = filter a by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"3 year ago\"..\"current year\"]; a = filter a by 'IsClosed' == \"true\"; a = filter a by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; a = group a by ('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month','CloseDate_Day');  a = foreach a generate 'CloseDate_Year' + \"~~~\" + 'CloseDate_Month' as 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month', sum('CloseDate_day_epoch') - sum('CreatedDate_day_epoch') as 'Days_Open'; a = foreach a generate 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month' as 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month', avg('Days_Open') as 'avg_Days_Open';","measures":[["avg","Days_Open"]],"groups":[["CloseDate_Year","CloseDate_Month"]]}

{"measures":[["sum","percent"]],"pigql":"q = load \"opportunity5\"; q = filter q by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; this_year = filter q by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year\"..\"current day\"]; last_year = filter q by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year - 1 year\"..\"current day - 1 year\"]; this_year = foreach this_year generate avg('Amount') as 'Amount'; last_year = foreach last_year generate avg('Amount') as 'Amount'; result = group this_year by all full, last_year by all; result = foreach result generate (avg(this_year['Amount']) - avg(last_year['Amount']))/avg(last_year['Amount']) as 'sum_percent', avg(last_year['Amount'])  as 'last_year'; result = foreach result generate (case when 'sum_percent' < 0 then \"#E3193B\" when 'sum_percent' > 0 then \"#067D1E\" else \"#192B61\" end) as 'color', 'sum_percent' as 'sum_percent', 'last_year';"}

query.query: {"measures":[["avg","Days_Open"]],"pigql":"a = load \"opportunity5\"; a = filter a by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year\"..\"current day\"]; a = filter a by 'IsClosed' == \"true\"; a = filter a by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; a = foreach a generate sum('CloseDate_day_epoch') - sum('CreatedDate_day_epoch') as 'Days_Open'; a = group a by all; a = foreach a generate avg('Days_Open') as 'avg_Days_Open';"}

{"measures":[["sum","percent"]],"pigql":"q = load \"opportunity5\"; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == \"true\"; q = filter q by 'IsWon' == \"true\"; a = filter q by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year - 1 year\"..\"current day - 1 year\"]; b = filter q by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year\"..\"current day\"]; a = foreach a generate sum('CloseDate_day_epoch') - sum('CreatedDate_day_epoch') as 'Days_Open'; b = foreach b generate sum('CloseDate_day_epoch') - sum('CreatedDate_day_epoch') as 'Days_Open'; c = group a by all full, b by all; c = foreach c generate avg(a.'Days_Open') as 'A', avg(b.'Days_Open') as 'B'; c = foreach c generate (B-A)/A as 'sum_percent', A as 'last_year'; c = foreach c generate (case when 'sum_percent' > 0 then \"#E3193B\" when 'sum_percent' < 0 then \"#067D1E\" else \"#192B61\" end) as 'color', 'sum_percent' as 'sum_percent','last_year' as 'last_year';","groups":[]}

{"measures":[["sum","percent"]],"pigql":"q = load \"opportunity5\"; q = filter q by 'IsWon' == \"true\";this_year = filter q by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year\"..\"current day\"];last_year = filter q by date('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [\"current year - 1 year\"..\"current day - 1 year\"]; this_year = foreach this_year generate sum('Amount') as 'Amount';last_year = foreach last_year generate sum('Amount') as 'Amount';result = group this_year by all full, last_year by all; result = foreach result generate (sum(this_year['Amount']) - sum(last_year['Amount']))/sum(last_year['Amount']) as 'sum_percent', sum(last_year['Amount']) as 'last_year'; result = foreach result generate 'sum_percent','last_year', (case when 'sum_percent' > 0 then \"#067D1E\" when 'sum_percent' < 0 then \"#E3193B\" else \"#192B61\" end) as 'color';"}
